MSP (Merchant Servicing Portal) is widely used to servicing the Domestic and International Merchants. MSP is capable of servicing Financial & Non-financial
data manipulation and maintenance of a Merchants. The data handled in MSP are stored in SOR (System of Record) and tracking details are stored 
in MTD (Merchant Tracking Database). MSP consuming data in following ways. Data Power – DP Service, Application Program Interface – API Service,
IBM Stored Procedures. MSP application is based on Pega and One Servicing Technologies.  MSP is capable of servicing below Intents/Demands. 

Merchant Tracking
Audit Details
Contact History
Memo
Communication
Communication History
Financial Details
Banking Details
Banking Approval
Payments
Long Term Reserve
Merchant Details
Business Contact
Characteristics
Entity Details
